title: New: Chase & Status – Count On Me (Feat. Moko)
content:
I’ll be honest, I’m not huge on Chase & Status, but this track featuring our girl Moko is pretty special.

With a rapidly growing fanbase, and rumours of a record deal having been signed, you can expect to be hearing Moko’s name A LOT more over the coming months. There’s a real old school vibe to Count On Me, whilst fitting perfectly into the ‘club-ready’ bracket. Check out Count On Me below, released 29 September.
